Patch an MCP server manifest

Usage:
  mcp-runtime server patch [name] [flags]

Flags:
  -h, --help                help for patch
      --namespace string    Namespace (default "mcp-servers")
      --patch string        Inline JSON/YAML patch document
      --patch-file string   Path to a JSON/YAML patch document
      --type string         Patch type (merge|json|strategic) (default "merge")

Global Flags:
      --debug      Enable debug mode with structured error logging
      --use-kube   Use kubectl and local kubeconfig instead of the platform API for supported commands
